Bio-Retinol: all you need to know! 

Title- How to use Bio Retinol 

1. RIGHT AGE TO START WITH RETINOL 

SOLUTION- Most dermatologists advise introducing retinol into your skincare routine in your mid 20's, 
Add Bio-Retinol in your skincare regime now. It is suitable for all skin types 

2. WHAT IS BIO-RETINOL?
Bio-Retinol is a powerful plant derivative of Vitamin A which -
- Tackles signs of ageing
- Corrects pigmentation
- Fights breakouts
- Improves skin elasticity and firmness
- Boosts skin radiance

Shots of lotus products in a nice layout

3. Application-
Morning clip- 
Using the Lotus Botanicals Bio Retinol Ultra Crème.

Night clip- layering my skin with the sleeping mask

Pro tip- never skip your sunscreen the next morning as this aids cell turnover. 

Lastly, don’t ever mix retinol with vitamin C and chemical exfoliants like AHA BHA
